parameters: You don't have to be so silent about it, Elena.
\nr<Virya>Just tell me why. \.\.I need to hear it from you.
\nr<Virya>She is. \.Don't dodge the question. \.What were you thinking?
\nr<Elena>I really don't know. \.I probably just did it.
\nr<Virya>Don't lie to me. \.You're not the kind of girl to just lash out at someone spontaneously,
Something happened with her and Saras, but I don't know what.
